# Traceability Rules

Bidirectional links — maintain in `5-dev/traceability.md` and source files.

## ID conventions

| ID | Defined in |
|----|------------|
| `GOL-##`, `STK-##` | `stakeholders-and-goals.md` |
| `SCN-##`, `EVT-##` | `business-scenarios.md` |
| `UR-F##-##`, `FR-F##-##` | `2-features/F##_*.md` |
| `NFR-##`, `ADR-##` | `solution-strategy.md` |
| `F##` | `features-list.md` (derived from `GOL-##` / `SCN-##` per [02-features-list.mdc](02-features-list.mdc)) |
| `BB-##` | `building-blocks.md` |
| `RT-##` | `runtime-views.md` |
| `BL-##`, `TC-##` | `backlog.md`, `testing-plan.md` |
| `Q-S##`, `Q-F##-##`, `Q-A##`, `Q-D##`, `Q-V##` | `open-questions.md` |
| `MCK-##`, `JRN-##`, `CMP-##`, `DSA-##` | `mockups.md`, `user-journeys.md`, `design-strategy.md` |

## Primary chain

```
GOL → SCN → UR-F##-## → FR-F##-## → F## → BL-## → TC-##
```

1. Every `UR` → ≥1 `GOL` or `SCN`
2. Every `FR` → ≥1 `UR` (or `NFR` when Type is non-functional)
3. Every user-facing feature → ≥1 UR and ≥1 FR
4. `features-list` **Summary** ↔ feature **Overview** intent (primary UR once spec exists)
5. UI/runtime flows reference `FR-F##-##`; backlog AC verifiable against FR
6. Tests reference FR or UR they verify

## Cross-cutting chain

```
NFR ↔ F## ↔ FR ↔ TC
ADR ↔ BB ↔ F##
RT ↔ BB ↔ F## / SCN
```

NFR/ADR bidirectional links; Quality Goals → NFR; each `RT-##` lists BB + F##/SCN.

## Feature dependencies

| Rule | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| Direct deps only | **Requires** lists immediate prerequisites |
| Hard gate | All **Requires** must be **Implemented** before feature **In development** |
| Sync | Frontmatter `requires`, Overview **Requires**, dependency diagram match |
| No cycles | Invalid — split or merge features |

## When to update traceability

| Change | Update |
|--------|--------|
| Goal/scenario | Feature UR; `traceability.md` |
| UR/FR | `features-list` **Summary**; backlog; `traceability.md` |
| NFR/ADR | Features; `solution-strategy.md` per [04-solution-strategy.mdc](04-solution-strategy.mdc); `building-blocks.md`; `traceability.md` |
| Backlog / test | `traceability.md` row; feature **Status** when backlog state changes |
